{"title":"Bolt of Cold","url":"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/Bolt_of_Cold","type":"markdown","data":"***Version [0.30](/0.30 \"0.30\")**: This article **may not be** up to date for the [latest stable release](/0.32 \"0.32\") of Crawl.*\n\n|   |                                    |\n| - | ---------------------------------- |\n|   | Fires a penetrating bolt of frost. |\n\n**Bolt of Cold** is a monster-only spell capable of striking multiple targets along its path, doing a considerable amount of cold damage. [Cold resistance](/Cold#Cold_Resistance \"Cold\") reduces the damage dealt by this spell by 50% (rC+), 66% (rC++), or 80% (rC+++). The [Cold Breath](/Cold_Breath \"Cold Breath\") monster ability is very similar to this spell.\n\nBolts of cold that travel through [water](/Water \"Water\") will create [freezing vapours](/Freezing_vapour \"Freezing vapour\").\n\nThe following enemies cast Bolt of Cold:\n\n- p [![Arcanist.png](/images/8/87/Arcanist.png)](/File:Arcanist.png) **[Arcanist](/Arcanist \"Arcanist\")** (3d18 damage)\n- 2 [![Blizzard demon.png](/images/2/25/Blizzard_demon.png)](/File:Blizzard_demon.png) **[Blizzard demon](/Blizzard_demon \"Blizzard demon\")** (3d21 damage)\n- n [![Bog body.png](/images/0/09/Bog_body.png)](/File:Bog_body.png) **[Bog body](/Bog_body \"Bog body\")** (3d18 damage)\n- L [![Boris.png](/images/4/46/Boris.png)](/File:Boris.png) **[Boris](/Boris \"Boris\")** (3d32 damage)\n- q [![Draconian knight.png](/images/a/a6/Draconian_knight.png)](/File:Draconian_knight.png) **[Draconian knight](/Draconian_knight \"Draconian knight\")** (3d25 damage)\n- & [![Ereshkigal.png](/images/a/a8/Ereshkigal.png)](/File:Ereshkigal.png) **[Ereshkigal](/Ereshkigal \"Ereshkigal\")** (3d27 damage)\n- e [![Fannar.png](/images/4/49/Fannar.png)](/File:Fannar.png) **[Fannar](/Fannar \"Fannar\")** (3d18 damage)\n- C [![Frost giant.png](/images/7/74/Frost_giant.png)](/File:Frost_giant.png) **[Frost giant](/Frost_giant \"Frost giant\")** (3d25 damage)\n- D [![Golden dragon.png](/images/3/36/Golden_dragon.png)](/File:Golden_dragon.png) **[Golden dragon](/Golden_dragon \"Golden dragon\")** (3d27 damage)\n- L [![Halazid warlock.png](/images/d/d2/Halazid_warlock.png)](/File:Halazid_warlock.png) **[Halazid warlock](/Halazid_warlock \"Halazid warlock\")** (3d27 damage)\n- 1 [![Ice Fiend.png](/images/a/a8/Ice_Fiend.png)](/File:Ice_Fiend.png) **[Ice Fiend](/Ice_Fiend \"Ice Fiend\")** (3d27 damage)\n- 8 [![Ice statue.png](/images/4/49/Ice_statue.png)](/File:Ice_statue.png) **[Ice statue](/Ice_statue \"Ice statue\")** (3d16 damage)\n- L [![Lich.png](/images/8/86/Lich.png)](/File:Lich.png) **[Lich](/Lich \"Lich\")** (3d29 damage)\n- Q [![Tengu reaver.png](/images/2/24/Tengu_reaver.png)](/File:Tengu_reaver.png) **[Tengu reaver](/Tengu_reaver \"Tengu reaver\")** (3d26 damage)\n\nThe following enemies may be able to cast Bolt of Cold, depending on their spell set:\n\n- & [![Pandemonium lord.png](/images/c/c6/Pandemonium_lord.png)](/File:Pandemonium_lord.png) **[Pandemonium lord](/Pandemonium_lord \"Pandemonium lord\")** (5.2% chance)\n\n## History\n\n| [![Bolt of cold.png](/images/d/d1/Bolt_of_cold.png)](/File:Bolt_of_cold.png) Bolt of Cold |                                                                                            |\n| :---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ |\n| Level                                                                                     | 6                                                                                          |\n| School1                                                                                   | [Conjuration](/Conjurations \"Conjurations\")                                                |\n| School2                                                                                   | [Ice](/Ice_Magic \"Ice Magic\")                                                              |\n| Source(s)                                                                                 | - [Book of Ice](/Book_of_Ice \"Book of Ice\")\n- [Wand of cold](/Wand_of_cold \"Wand of cold\") |\n| [Casting noise](/Spell_noise \"Spell noise\")                                               | 6                                                                                          |\n| [Spell noise](/Spell_noise \"Spell noise\")                                                 | 6                                                                                          |\n\n| Spell Details                           |                                    |\n| :-------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------- |\n| Damage Formula                          | 6d(3+Power/9) [cold](/Cold \"Cold\") |\n| Max Damage                              | 6d(25)                             |\n| [Max Power](/Spell_power \"Spell power\") | 200                                |\n| Range                                   | 5                                  |\n| Targeting                               | Bolt                               |\n| To-hit                                  | 10+Power/25                        |\n| Special                                 | N/A                                |\n\n- Prior to [0.26](/0.26 \"0.26\"), [bolt spells](/Bolt_spell \"Bolt spell\") would decrease by 1 range for every target they hit.\n- Prior to [0.25](/0.25 \"0.25\"), Bolt of Cold was a level 6 [Conjurations](/Conjurations \"Conjurations\")/[Ice Magic](/Ice_Magic \"Ice Magic\") spell available to players.\n\n* It was often considered worse than [Bolt of Fire](/Bolt_of_Fire \"Bolt of Fire\"), due to its inferior range, and the fact that cold resistant monsters were generally more common ([undead](/Undead \"Undead\") have rC+, for instance).\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset